#This file contains the beautifu monitor toolkits we can find
#Contribute your toolkit in the format: toolkit_name, toolkit_description(short description), toolkit_website
Collectd, To collect the performance metrics on the system level, http://collectd.org/
Grafana, To beautiful and powerful metric dashbord and graph editor, http://grafana.org/
InfluxDB, To store the performance metric time series data, https://influxdb.com/
OpenTSDB, To store the time series data, http://opentsdb.net/

